{"tid":1791043,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港鐵：明天元朗區有公眾活動，元朗站下午一時起會關閉","createTime":"2019-12-20T12:46:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-20T12:58:29.000Z","uid":91914,"like":6,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"02f8c575ebc2499dcb0c5e710f97cf7be2d86833","tid":1791043,"uid":91914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T12:46:21.000Z","msg":"2010 #港鐵 #元朗站 #交通消息 <br />\n<br />\n港鐵表示，因應在元朗區有公眾活動進行，經詳細風險評估及與相關政府部門商討後，考慮到乘客、員工及鐵路運作安全，明天（12月21日）下午1時起，西鐵綫服務作出以下調整：<br />\n<br />\n&bull; 元朗站將暫時關閉，列車不停元朗站<br />\n&bull; 港鐵將提供免費接駁巴士，來往元朗站至朗屏站接載乘客<br />\n<br />\n港鐵會繼續評估風險狀況，並會在有需要時臨時關閉個別車站或暫停個別路段的列車服務。<br />\n#now"},{"pid":"57fbfc36289e114f94c118ef61368e3508aff6d2","tid":1791043,"uid":91914,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T12:47:43.000Z","msg":"港鐵幫手搞活動<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ece3f8388d5a5cf7c6e5646324d88571baf50fa","tid":1791043,"uid":91914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T12:48:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b90b466e735ba2af6fc51cfb69d28f466116260","tid":1791043,"uid":91914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T12:49:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8c42fd840ce446f45877da4568956cd5d67b74f","tid":1791043,"uid":91914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T12:50:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/argue.gif\" class=\"hkg